ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectNational Capital Commission - Public Service Alliance of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the National Capital Commission (NCC) to ENTER into a COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the Public Service Alliance of Canada (PSAC), beginning January 1, 2015 and ending December 31, 2018, that covers all employees in the bargaining unit of the NCC.
